snippet.title: Crazy Time Traveler Arrives in Diner Scene - GOOD LUCK, HAVE FUN, DON'T DIE (2026) Sam Rockwell
snippet.description:
Official Good Luck, Have Fun, Don't Die Movie Clip & Trailer 2026 | App ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/App | Sam Rockwell Movie Trailer | Cinema: 13 Feb 2026 | More https://KinoCheck.com/movie/bi4/good-luck-have-fun-dont-die?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=description
The narrative unravels within the confines of a diner, where an odd newcomer alleging to hail from the future makes his entrance. He alerts the patrons about a mission they must embark on with him to avert an artificial intelligence from taking over. Skeptical of his claims, the diners wrestle with the notion that their existence could be a mere simulation.

Good Luck, Have Fun, Don't Die (2026) is the new science fiction movie by Gore Verbinski, starring Sam Rockwell, Zazie Beetz and Michael Peña.
